        <title>Linux bridge mechanism driver</title>
        <paragraph>The Linux bridge mechanism driver uses only Linux bridges and <literal>veth</literal> pairs
            as interconnection devices. A layer-2 agent manages Linux bridges on each
            compute node and any other node that provides layer-3 (routing), DHCP,
            metadata, or other network services.</paragraph>
